## Proposed Layout Change

The Overview page currently has this grid structure:

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────┐
│  Score Gauge + Risk Badge (col-5)   │ Flagged (2)  │
├───────┬───────┬───────┬───────┬─────┴──────────────┤
│ Total │ Risky │ NLP   │ Avg   │ Risk Ratio         │
│Clause │Clause │Cleared│Sever. │                    │
├───────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┤
│ Risk Profile          │ Analysis Depth             │
├───────────────────────┬────────────────────────────┤
│ Risk Breakdown Radar  │ Key Risk Factors           │
└───────────────────────┴────────────────────────────┘
```

**After enhancement:**

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  ✨ AI Narrative Verdict (full-width card)          │
├─────────────────────────────────────┬───────────────┤
│  Score Gauge + Risk Badge (col-5)   │ Flagged (2)   │
├───────┬───────┬───────┬─────────────┴───────────────┤
│ Total │ Risky │ NLP   │ Risk Ratio                  │
│Clause │Clause │Cleared│                             │
├─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────┤
│  📊 Severity Histogram  │  🔍 How We Analyzed       │
│  (bars by tier + avg)   │  (NLP vs Deep AI funnel)  │
├─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────┤
│ Risk Profile            │ Analysis Depth            │
├─────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────┤
│ Risk Breakdown Radar    │ Key Risk Factors          │
└─────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────┘
```

> [!NOTE]
> The old "Avg Severity" stat card is **removed** from the 5-card row and replaced by the full histogram card in the new row. The 5-card row becomes a 4-card row.

